## API Endpoints Summary

| Group | Base URL | Auth |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | `POST /api/auth/login` | Public |
| Auth | `POST /api/auth/register` | Public |
| Auth | `GET /api/auth/me` | Token |
| Patients | `GET /api/users/patients` | Doctor/Admin |
| Doctors | `GET /api/users/doctors` | Any logged-in |
| Appointments | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/appointments` | Role-filtered |
| Therapies | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/therapies` | Role-filtered |
| Invoices | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/invoices` | Doctor/Admin |
| Feedback | `GET/POST /api/feedback` | Role-filtered |
| Feedback reply | `PUT /api/feedback/:id/reply` | Doctor |
